               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction&#xD; - Maqdǝma Wangel “Introduction to the Gospels”
                     (fols. 3ra-6ra)&#xD; - The “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 6ra-6rb)&#xD; - On the
                     reliability of the Gospels (fol. 6rb)&#xD; - Biography of Matthew (fols.
                     6rb-6va)&#xD; - Statement about the Eusebian sections (fol. 6va)&#xD; - Canon
                     Tables (fols. 6vb-10rb)&#xD; II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 10va-48va)&#xD; -
                     List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 70 titles (fols.
                     10va-10vb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 11ra-48rb)&#xD; -
                     Postscript (fols. 48rb-48va)&#xD; III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 48va-73rb)&#xD; -
                     Biography of Mark (fols. 48va-48vb)&#xD; - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel
                     of Mark: 48 titles (fols. 49ra-49rb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark”
                     (fols. 50ra-73ra)&#xD; - Postscript (fols. 73ra-73rb)&#xD; IV) Gospel of Luke
                     (fols. 73rb-110rb)&#xD; - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 80
                     titles (fols. 73rb-73vb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Luqās “Gospel of Luke” (fols.
                     74ra-110rb)&#xD; - Postscript (f. 110rb)&#xD; V) Gospel of John (fols.
                     110rb-138va)&#xD; - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 20 titles
                     (fols. 110rb-110vb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols.
                     110vb-138rb)&#xD; - Postscript (fols. 138rb-138va)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-2;
                     colophon.</summary>
